text: Nurses is a Canadian medical drama television series that premiered on Global on January 6, 2020. The series centers on a group of nurses at a busy downtown Toronto hospital. Nurses was created by much of the same team behind the series Rookie Blue, including Ilana Frank, Adam Pettle, Vanessa Piazza and Tassie Cameron. ==Cast and characters== ===Main=== * Tiera Skovbye as Grace Knight * Natasha Calis as Ashley Collins * Jordan Johnson-Hinds as Keon Colby * Sandy Sidhu as Nazneen Khan * Donald Maclean Jr. as Wolf Burke ===Recurring=== * Cathy White as Sinead O’Rourke * Ryan-James Hatanaka as Dr. Evan Wallace * Nicola Correia-Damude as Dr. Vanessa Banks * Alexandra Ordolis as Caro ==Episodes== ==International== From May 2020 onwards the series was broadcast by Net5 in the Netherlands. ==References== ==External links== * * * Nurses at epguides Category:2020 Canadian television series debuts Category:2020s Canadian drama television series Category:2020s Canadian LGBT- related drama television series Category:Canadian medical television series Category:English-language television shows Category:Lesbian-related television shows Category:Television series produced in Toronto Category:Television shows set in Toronto Category:Global Television Network original programming
